OL,3,CWhat does ITV News poll mean ahead of
OL,4,CThursday's election in Wales?
OL,6,FTuesday's YouGov poll for ITV Wales
OL,7,Freinforces what we've seen for several
OL,8,Fmonths, that it is either Plaid Cymru
OL,9,For Reform UK who look far more likely
OL,10,Fto lead the next Welsh government than
OL,11,FLabour, which has never lost a Senedd
OL,12,Felection.
OL,14,FAfter several polls showed the two
OL,15,Fparties neck and neck, the final
OL,16,Fsurvey before Thursday's vote suggests
OL,17,FPlaid are now projected to be the
OL,18,Flargest party, with their vote share
OL,19,Fincreasing from 29% to 33% since April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
