OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778033004
OL,3,CWhat does ITV News poll mean ahead of
OL,4,CThursday's election in Wales?
OL,6,FThat rise appears to have come largely
OL,7,Fat the expense of the Greens, whose
OL,8,Fsupport has fallen from 10% to 8%.
OL,10,FReform UK are polling at 29%, with
OL,11,FWelsh Labour on 12%, the Welsh
OL,12,FConservatives on 9%, and the Liberal
OL,13,FDemocrats on 6%.
OL,15,FThat will provide a welcome boost for
OL,16,FPlaid Cymru but the margins remain
OL,17,Fvery tight, and the outcome far from
OL,18,Fcertain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
