OL,3,CWhat does ITV News poll mean ahead of
OL,4,CThursday's election in Wales?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn fact, that uncertainty is greater
OL,12,Fthan in previous Welsh elections,
OL,13,Flargely because of the new,
OL,14,Fproportional voting system.
OL,16,FVoters will elect six members in each
OL,17,Fof sixteen large constituencies under
OL,18,Fwhat's known as the D'Hondt system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
