OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778033004
OL,3,CWhat does ITV News poll mean ahead of
OL,4,CThursday's election in Wales?
OL,6,FIt's a method which makes it
OL,7,Fnotoriously difficult to predict who
OL,8,Fwill get the fifth and sixth seats in
OL,9,Feach constituency because the margins
OL,10,Fare very tight.
OL,12,FThis means small changes in support
OL,13,Fare likely to have a disproportionate
OL,14,Fimpact on how many Senedd members each
OL,15,Fparty returns.
OL,17,FThat is particularly true for parties
OL,18,Flike Labour, the Conservatives and the
OL,19,FGreens, due to the level of support
OL,20,Fthey're receiving in recent polls.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
