OL,3,CWhat does ITV News poll mean ahead of
OL,4,CThursday's election in Wales?
OL,6,FIt is also worth noting that even this
OL,7,Fresult would leave Plaid Cymru short
OL,8,Fof an outright majority.
OL,10,FThe usual caveats apply when relying
OL,11,Fon any single poll.
OL,13,FBut taken alongside other recent
OL,14,Fsurveys, there is a consistent
OL,15,Fpicture: the race to become the
OL,16,Flargest party is now primarily between
OL,17,FPlaid Cymru and Reform UK, with the
OL,18,Fother four main parties some distance
OL,19,Fbehind.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
