OL,3,CWhat does ITV News poll mean ahead of
OL,4,CThursday's election in Wales?
OL,6,FAfter a century of Labour hegemony in
OL,7,FWales, this would be an historic
OL,8,Fresult in arguably the most
OL,9,Fconsequential election in Welsh
OL,10,Fpolitical history.
